<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Na Hun Na Mangpha Na</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw hun leh kumhaw chu,
 Ni chengin a bei zel;
 Mi neizo leh mi lopite,
 Sang tamtak a liem tau;
 I nunnawp leh kipah niu le,
 Muol a liem tau hungkit lo din.

[V2]
 2. I chapan lai niu leh ,
 I vanglai niuhaw kha;
 Gel kitin lung a suhel ngei,
 Lunggil mei bang a zing;
 Ngai u heng la, sam mahleu hing,
 Muol aliem tau hung kitlo di'n.

[V3]
 3. Khawvel sumhaw cheng le,
 Giel banga mang thei ui;
 Khawvel pumpi nei mah leng le,
 I lung awi diek puona;
 Hunin muol liem pih zelin tin,
 Al bang vaihna phat a hihsau.

[V4]
 4. Ziehi chu ei dawng tie,
 Na hun na mangpha nam?
 Thilpha bawlin, gitloh doin,
 Hinna lam dik hawhin;
 Chun kumsawt nawpna neiin la,
 Phat zatchuom tak lohna achun.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>153</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
</song>